# PHASE 3 COMPLETE

## Status: ✅ FINISHED

All Phase 3 features (14-17) have been implemented successfully.

## Features Completed:

### Feature 14: Data Backup (Export/Import)
- ✅ GET /api/v1/backup/export - Returns all user data as JSON
- ✅ POST /api/v1/backup/import - Accepts JSON, validates, imports
- Database migrations: backup_metadata, transaction tags support

### Feature 15: Duplicate Detection
- ✅ GET /api/v1/duplicates/detect - Find transactions with same amount/date/description
- ✅ POST /api/v1/duplicates/action - Mark/delete duplicate pairs
- ✅ POST /api/v1/transactions/merge - Merge selected duplicates
- SQL pattern: GROUP BY amount, date, description with similarity matching

### Feature 16: Goals Tracking  
- ✅ goals table (target_amount, current_amount, deadline, category_id)
- ✅ Simple progress bar display via API
- ✅ Calculate current_amount from transactions
- Endpoints: CRUD operations + contribute endpoint

### Feature 17: Cash Flow Calendar
- ✅ Group transactions by date
- ✅ Calculate daily net (income - expenses)
- ✅ Color-code: green (positive), red (negative)
- ✅ Display as calendar grid via API

## Implementation Notes:
- Reused existing db connection pattern
- Followed established codebase patterns
- No encryption for backup (stretch goal noted)
- Simple working code over perfect architecture

